县议会分区與税务分区並沒有直接關係，因為税务分区的人口分佈並不平均。希洛和科哈拉地區人口比較多，而其他地區人口則比較少。<ref>{{cite web |title= Hawai{{okina}}i County Council |work= official web site |url= http://www.co.hawaii.hi.us/council/districts.htm |access-date= 2013-01-20 |dead-url= yes |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110708080958/http://www.co.hawaii.hi.us/council/districts.htm |archive-date= 2011-07-08 }}</ref>

一些在其他州份屬於州政府的职能，夏威夷縣都擁有。例如，夏威夷縣擁有自己的酒类管制部。<ref>{{cite web |title = Office of Liquor Control |work= Hawaii County web site |url= http://www.hawaii-county.com/directory/dir_liquor.htm |access-date= 2013-01-20 |dead-url= yes |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101123054034/http://hawaii-county.com/directory/dir_liquor.htm |archive-date= 2010-11-23 }}</ref>

===州政府===
以往，[[夏威夷公共安全部|夏威夷公共安全部]]是負責[[库拉尼惩教设施|库拉尼惩教设施]]的运作<ref>"[http://hawaii.gov/psd/corrections/institutions-division/prisons/kulani-correctional-facility Kulani Correctional Facility] {{Wayback|url=http://hawaii.gov/psd/corrections/institutions-division/prisons/kulani-correctional-facility |date=20120813085121 }}." [[Hawaii_Department_of_Public_Safety|Hawaii Department of Public Safety]]</ref>。2009年，夏威夷公共安全部宣佈關閉库拉尼惩教设施<ref>"[http://hawaii.gov/gov/news/files/2009/july/psd-to-close-kulani-prison-facility-to-help-at-risk-youth Closure of Kulani Saves $2.8M Annually; Facility to Help At-Risk Youth]." Hawaii Department of Public Safety. 2009-7. </ref>。

